WEBVTT

00:10:29.582 --> 00:10:31.190
na nadzorovalno državo,

00:10:31.190 --> 00:10:33.354
ki ni opazovala vsakogar ves čas,

00:10:33.354 --> 00:10:35.407
ampak kjer so se ljudje zavedali,

00:10:35.407 --> 00:10:37.036
da so lahko opazovani kadarkoli.

00:10:37.036 --> 00:10:40.110
Orwellov pripovedovalec Winston Smith

00:10:40.110 --> 00:10:42.150
je njihov sistem nadzora

00:10:42.150 --> 00:10:43.548
opisal takole:

00:10:43.548 --> 00:10:45.975
"Seveda ni bilo mogoče vedeti,

00:10:45.975 --> 00:10:48.292
ali te v danem trenutku opazujejo."

00:10:48.292 --> 00:10:49.743
Nadaljeval je:

00:10:49.743 --> 00:10:51.454
"... priključili so se lahko na

00:10:51.454 --> 00:10:53.163
tvoj oddajnik, kadarkoli so hoteli.

00:10:53.163 --> 00:10:55.742
Živeti si moral — in si živel,

00:10:55.742 --> 00:10:57.995
iz navade, ki se je spremenila v nagon —

00:10:57.995 --> 00:11:00.490
v domnevi, da prisluškujejo